Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.70,0:00:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別篇  其之一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.79,0:00:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東的家\N這是某天所發生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小東東念書中——\N寫啊寫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～哇～\N杉樹花粉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咻！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橡皮擦\N為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.16,0:00:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈…段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.09,0:00:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.14,0:00:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠你今天也很用功呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴著眼鏡！這、這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.54,0:01:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是男朋友給的嗎…  哇——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.54,0:01:13.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先擱下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑啊跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.32,0:01:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑啊跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑啊跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.80,0:01:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forever～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forever～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.06,0:01:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘原來是你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放過我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃閃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能這樣對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.47,0:01:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.93,0:01:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔噢噢噢噢噢噢噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:02:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是兜襠布
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  小鞘…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挺不過月末了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.46,0:02:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…呵呵呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.61,0:02:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這眼鏡是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.45,0:02:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:12.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要現金的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛啊飛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛啊飛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這炸肉餅給小東東送去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:34.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒注意到眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等？剛剛有小東東的味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯覺吧  快給她送去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天\N叮噹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:42.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸肉餅  給小東東  BY 紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:47.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一整天沒注意到丟了眼鏡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我的眼鏡？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻啊翻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.89,0:02:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
